<div id="review_386102370" class="review nosyndicate" itemprop="reviews" itemscope itemtype="http://schema.org/Review">
  <link itemprop="url" href="https://www.goodreads.com/review/show/386102370" />
    <a title="cEe beE" class="left imgcol" href="/user/show/9897162-cee-bee"><img alt="cEe beE" src="https://images.gr-assets.com/users/1428533712p2/9897162.jpg" /></a>

  <div class="left bodycol">
    <div class="reviewHeader uitext stacked">
        <a class="reviewDate createdAt right" href="/review/show/386102370?book_show_action=true">Aug 07, 2012</a>

      <span itemprop="author" itemscope itemtype="http://schema.org/Person">
        <a title="cEe beE" class="user" itemprop="url" name="cEe beE" href="/user/show/9897162-cee-bee">cEe beE</a>
      </span>

        rated it
        <span class=" staticStars notranslate" title="did not like it"><span size="15x15" class="staticStar p10">did not like it</span><span size="15x15" class="staticStar p0"></span><span size="15x15" class="staticStar p0"></span><span size="15x15" class="staticStar p0"></span><span size="15x15" class="staticStar p0"></span></span>

          <span class="greyText">&nbsp;&middot;&nbsp;</span>
          <a class="lightGreyText" title="Paperback 9781442409064" href="/book/show/11733134-wither">review of another edition</a>


        

          <div class="uitext greyText bookshelves">
            Shelves:
              <a class="actionLinkLite" href="/review/list/9897162-cee-bee?shelf=wtf">wtf</a>, 
              <a class="actionLinkLite" href="/review/list/9897162-cee-bee?shelf=humor-is-absent">humor-is-absent</a>, 
              <a class="actionLinkLite" href="/review/list/9897162-cee-bee?shelf=hysterical-romance">hysterical-romance</a>, 
              <a class="actionLinkLite" href="/review/list/9897162-cee-bee?shelf=doesnt-make-sense">doesnt-make-sense</a>, 
              <a class="actionLinkLite" href="/review/list/9897162-cee-bee?shelf=r-u-effing-kidding-me">r-u-effing-kidding-me</a>, 
              <a class="actionLinkLite" href="/review/list/9897162-cee-bee?shelf=hunger-games-copy-cats">hunger-games-copy-cats</a>, 
              <a class="actionLinkLite" href="/review/list/9897162-cee-bee?shelf=dim-wit-heroines">dim-wit-heroines</a>, 
              <a class="actionLinkLite" href="/review/list/9897162-cee-bee?shelf=logic-thrown-out-the-window">logic-thrown-out-the-window</a>, 
              <a class="actionLinkLite" href="/review/list/9897162-cee-bee?shelf=moronic-couple">moronic-couple</a>, 
              <a class="actionLinkLite" href="/review/list/9897162-cee-bee?shelf=dystopia-hysteria">dystopia-hysteria</a>
          </div>
    </div>


        <div class="reviewText stacked">
              <span id="reviewTextContainer386102370" class="readable"
              >
            
<span id="freeTextContainer12084091164079234917">RECIPE FOR WITHER: a YA Dystopia:<br/><br/>1) Take plot elements from <b>&apos;The Handmaid&apos;s Tale&apos;</b> and <b>&apos;Stolen Innocence: My Story of Growing Up in a Polygamous Sect, Becoming a Teenage Bride&apos;</b>. Mix them together. <i>Caution: It will be messy.</i><br/><br/>2) Set the story in the future where science has eradicated cancer, allergies and STDs but dooms the next generation to live shorter lives. 25 years for males and only 20 for women. <i>
  <u>
    <b>DO NOT give details, keep things vague.</b>
  </u>
</i><br/><br/>3) Put in a <b>dull and humorless female main ch</b></span>
  <span id="freeText12084091164079234917" style="display:none">RECIPE FOR WITHER: a YA Dystopia:<br /><br />1) Take plot elements from <b>'The Handmaid's Tale'</b> and <b>'Stolen Innocence: My Story of Growing Up in a Polygamous Sect, Becoming a Teenage Bride'</b>. Mix them together. <i>Caution: It will be messy.</i><br /><br />2) Set the story in the future where science has eradicated cancer, allergies and STDs but dooms the next generation to live shorter lives. 25 years for males and only 20 for women. <i>
  <u>
    <b>DO NOT give details, keep things vague.</b>
  </u>
</i><br /><br />3) Put in a <b>dull and humorless female main character</b>. Slowly add a long and meandering storyline that doesn't go anywhere. Also include a pointless romance with an equally boring male character.<br /><br />4) Add baffling info like north America is the only country left, after a world war wipes out the rest of humanity off the face of the earth. <i>Again, do not give any details. <u><b>No explanations are needed</b>.</u></i><br /><br />5) <b>Stir ingredients well until the story is <i>completely lacking in cohesion.</i> <br /><br />And voila, you have Wither!</b><br /><br /></span>
  <a data-text-id="12084091164079234917" href="#" onclick="swapContent($(this));; return false;">...more</a>

          </span>
