        <div class="reviewText stacked">
              <span id="reviewTextContainer117089289" class="readable"
              >
            
<span id="freeTextContainer2126093868378910152">I really don&apos;t think I&apos;m cut out for realistic dystopia. I think I should just stick with my survival type adrenalin rush reads like The Hunger Games and The Maze Runner.<br/><br/>Without a doubt, <b>Wither</b> is probably one of the most powerful dystopia YA reads of 2011.<br/>The plot is gripping, thought provoking and very distrubing. The writing, absolutely outstanding, but I just couldn&apos;t stomach the idea&apos;s in this one.<br/>Not for me...<br/><br/>(Arc provided through S&amp;S Galleygrab)</span>
  <span id="freeText2126093868378910152" style="display:none">I really don't think I'm cut out for realistic dystopia. I think I should just stick with my survival type adrenalin rush reads like The Hunger Games and The Maze Runner.<br /><br />Without a doubt, <b>Wither</b> is probably one of the most powerful dystopia YA reads of 2011.<br />The plot is gripping, thought provoking and very distrubing. The writing, absolutely outstanding, but I just couldn't stomach the idea's in this one.<br />Not for me...<br /><br />(Arc provided through S&amp;S Galleygrab)</span>
